:0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:16:23.000Z","msg":"雖然唔想咁講<br />\n但今次全球性爆發在所難免<br />\n搞唔好分分鐘有國家核平中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:26:25.000Z","msg":"連香港都會波及<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30149c10c05b8839dd8b9244a847dc29fc28024","tid":1839994,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaf2780e0600a70557a4fa94434119df52ca04d0","tid":1839994,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"237bc1f12b935a034f035a05edd30ce5d3428f8f","tid":1839994,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:16:23.000Z","msg":"雖然唔想咁講<br />\n但今次全球性爆發在所難免<br />\n搞唔好分分鐘有國家核平中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:26:25.000Z","msg":"連香港都會波及<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:38:33.000Z","msg":"我做沙盤推演下唔係主張，history never lies<br />\n你自己順住而家情況同我講嘅野諗落去就會明<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw我唔係住香港好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}